## Exit Codes

| Code | Meaning |
|------|---------|
| `0` | Success (may include warnings) |
| `1` | Failure (errors encountered) |
| `2` | Invalid arguments |
| `3` | Infrastructure connection failure (DB, broker, etc.) |

